reviewText: I expected it to be a movie, not just short episodes. Should have read closer.

Computer generated garbage!

Stick with the ORIGINAL Thomas the Tank Engine videos (not their computer-generated stuff).  Much better stories with morals.

Don't waste your money on this stuff.
Daughter loves videos, so that says it all.
Cute movie, my son loves it

My girls love Chuggington. This DVD contains five episodes from the Disney Jr. cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Snow Rescue Special
2. Iron Chuggers
3. Deputy Chug Patrollers
4. Movie Maker Brewster
5. Toot's Tall Tale

Bonus Features:
1. Badge Quest Episode: Wilson's Winter Feed
2. Character Montages: Fletch, Cormac and Tyne
3. Coloring and Activity Sheets
